; Regression test for issue #1602: Problem with "N" command (BZ#530)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1602
;
; The N directive marks a commodity as non-market, meaning it should be
; excluded from market-price valuations (-V/-X). Verify that amount_t::value()
; respects the COMMODITY_NOMARKET flag and does not convert via the price
; database.

N ACME

P 2020/06/01 ACME $75.00

2020/01/01 Buy ACME
    Assets:Investments   10 ACME @ $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal -V
            $-500.00
             10 ACME  Assets
            $-500.00    Cash
             10 ACME    Investments
--------------------
            $-500.00
             10 ACME
end test
